snippet.title: Kodukuhime
snippet.description: Produced by Nth Circle, Kodukuhime is a short kinetic novel inspired by retro shonen anime and manga, developed in one month for Battle Action Fantasy Jam 2023. Download for free here: https://nthcircle.itch.io/kodokuhime
